6:- `skills/cargo-agent/scripts/cargo-agent.sh`: Rust workflow runner sourcing `lib/x-agent-common.sh`; contains run_x step handlers and domain-specific helpers (jq diagnostics, package resolution, nextest).
7:- `skills/npm-agent/scripts/npm-agent.sh`: Node workflow runner sourcing `lib/x-agent-common.sh`; contains package-manager detection and file-scoping logic for lint/format.
8:- `skills/terra-agent/scripts/terra-agent.sh`: Terraform workflow runner sourcing `lib/x-agent-common.sh`; contains safe init/plan behavior and optional tflint checks.
11:- `tests/cargo-agent/flock/flock-test.sh`: validates lock wait behavior using a competing holder process and waiting-message assertions.
